  "learningOutcomes": [
    "Students will be able to state that Robert Hooke discovered cells in cork in 1665.",
    "Students will differentiate between Prokaryotic and Eukaryotic cells based on the presence of a nucleus.",
    "Students will explain why cells are considered the structural and functional units of life."
